help.description: Returns the list of command modules or gives you the description and usage for a selected command.

overwatch.description: Shows the Overwatch statistics of inputed Battle.Net ID. (Warning: Case Sensitive)

bnsstats.description: The Blade and Soul module provides in-depth character information.

echo.description: Repeats the given text. (Bot Owner Only)

gelbooru.description: Searches GelBooru for selected tags, if no tags are specified, it gives a random image. If the wanted tag contains spaces type it with an underscore instead as spaces are used to separate multiple tags.

imdb.description: Searches the Internet Movie Database for a Title of your choice.

imgur.description: Searches through Imgur posts for the given title. Do remember that it is not Image-Only

itad.description: Lists the latest deals from IsThereAnyDeal

joke.description: Outputs a random joke from a random source, it is totally cancerous.

startkaraoke.description: Starts the Karaoke function on a specified Voice Channel. The voice channel will then be put in Strict Mode that will enforce an Absolute Mute (Server Mute that can not be deactivated untill the function is deactivated).(All Karaoke Functions are Only for Specially Permitted Users)

karaokestrict.description: Toggles the Karaoke Strict Mode On and Off

handup.description: Adds you to the Singer Queue.

handdown.description: Removes you from the Singer Queue.

repertoire.description: Lists all the users in the Singer Queue

karaokeremove.description: Removes mentioned user from the Singer Queue

takemic.description: If it is your turn to sing, it will unmute you during the karaoke session and mute everyone else.

dropmic.description: Marks you ending your singing session. Allows the next person in the Singing Queue to pick the mic up.

karaokestatus.description: Outputs the current Karaoke Mode, Session Ongoing state, Channel for the Karaoke Session if running, and if the Karaoke is in Strict Mode.

forceunmute.description: A Testing Purpose function for forcing the channel to unmute all users.

forcemute.description: A Testing Purpose function for forcing the channel to mute all users.

listchannelmembers.description: A Testing Purpose function for listing all users in a voice channel.

setchannel.description: Sets the karaoke channel to a new specified channel.

signup.description: Signs you up for a karaoke event. Like saying you will be attending.

karaokelist.description: List all users that signed up for a karaoke event.

lastfm.description: List the users top tracks from LastFM.

league.description: Shows the players League of Legends statistics of inputed Summoner Name. You can also place a gamemode between the Region and Summoner Name to get statistics for it.

anime.description: Searches MyAnimeList for anime by given name. Generates a really cool image with the details!

manga.description: Searches MyAnimeList for manga by given name. Generates a really cool image with the details!

nhentai.description: Searches nHentai for doujinshi for the inputed name, displays the results, cover and tags.

jisho.description: Searches the Japanese word dictionary (Jisho) for the given word and gives information for it.

wanikani.description: Shows the WaniKani statistics of the person who used the command or a mentioned person. Also searches WaniKani for a given username. For advanced stats, a user must save his WaniKani API Key with the %pfx%wksave command. Use help on it to get more info.

wksave.description: Stores a given API Key or Username for you. If you want detailed stats when calling the %pfx%wanikani command you need to save your WK API Key like in the example bellow!

nsfwpermit.description: Permits the NSFW module in the channel where the command is written to. (Server Administrator Only)

osu.description: Generates a signature image with the users stats for osu.

pokemon.description: Shows details for the inputed Pokemon.

rule34.description: Searches Rule34 for selected tags, if no tags are specified, it gives a random image.

level.description: Shows yours or a mentioned persons Sigma level.

rip.description: Generates a tombstone with the mentioned users avatar.

ud.description: Shows the Urban Dictionary definition for the given word.

vndb.description: Searches the Visual Novel Database fot the title you inputed.

weather.description: Shows weather data for the selected location.

wowchar.description: Shows World of Warcraft Character information and equipment.

mtg.description: Searches the Magic The Gathering Database for the inputed card.
